Percolation Model.

Percolation Statistics This class provides methods for executing a Monte Carlo simulation of a percolating system.
PercolationStats(int, int) - Constructor for class PercolationStats
Creates a Monte Carlo Simulation Using a percolation grid model of size N, the simulation runs T trials recording the proportion of open sites before the system percolated.
